# -*- mode: emacs-news-view -*-

* (0.11.0) -- 2023.09.27

** Added
*** New 'kosz-ui' feature for interactive functions.

*** New 'kosz-build-build-docs' functions for build ".texi" files.

*** Downloading dependencies for test step.
Dependency packages will not appears in user's installed package list.

** Changed
*** Move interactive functions from other features to 'kosz-ui'.
'kosz-build-package'                -> 'kosz-ui-build-package'
'kosz-build-and-install-package'    -> 'kosz-ui-build-and-install-package'
'kosz-build-vc-package'             -> 'kosz-ui-build-vc-package'
'kosz-build-and-install-vc-package' -> 'kosz-ui-build-and-install-vc-package'
'kosz-test-package'                 -> 'kosz-ui-test-package'

*** API renames.
'kosz-build-build'            -> 'kosz-build-build-package'
'kosz-utils-validation-error' -> 'kosz-manifest-manifest-validation-error'

*** Properties what contain file paths should to contain relative paths.
"~", "/", ".", ".." in beggining of this properties trigger error.

*** Store builded package in "{root}/build-{pkgname}-{pkgversion}" directory.

*** Documentation improvement.

** Fixed
*** Processing "...-exclude" properties may trigger error.

*** Requiring unloaded features breaks manifest reading.

*** Manifest no longer readed as nil if it doesn't contain named properties.

* (0.10.1) -- 2023.09.13
Start changelog.
